#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="an4.25"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an4.25:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 4 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 4 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.25:0.2"
msgid "3. Uruvelavagga "
msgstr "3. At Uruvelā "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an4.25:0.3"
msgid "25. Brahmacariyasutta "
msgstr "25. The Spiritual Life "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "an4.25:1.1"
msgid "“Nayidaṃ, bhikkhave, brahmacariyaṃ vussati janakuhanatthaṃ, na janalapanatthaṃ, na lābhasakkārasilokānisaṃsatthaṃ, na itivādappamokkhānisaṃsatthaṃ, na ‘iti maṃ jano jānātū’ti. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, this spiritual life is not lived for the sake of deceiving people or flattering them, nor for the benefit of possessions, honor, or popularity, nor for the benefit of winning debates, nor thinking, ‘So let people know about me!’ "

msgctxt "an4.25:1.2"
msgid "Atha kho idaṃ, bhikkhave, brahmacariyaṃ vussati saṃvaratthaṃ pahānatthaṃ virāgatthaṃ nirodhatthanti. "
msgstr "This spiritual life is lived for the sake of restraint, giving up, fading away, and cessation. "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "an4.25:2.1"
msgid "Saṃvaratthaṃ pahānatthaṃ, "
msgstr "The Buddha taught the spiritual life "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an4.25:2.2"
msgid "brahmacariyaṃ anītihaṃ; "
msgstr "not because of tradition, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an4.25:2.3"
msgid "Adesayi so bhagavā, "
msgstr "but for the sake of restraint and giving up, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an4.25:2.4"
msgid "nibbānogadhagāminaṃ; "
msgstr "and because it culminates in extinguishment. "

# NOTE: Note that the reading mahattebhi, which I use as does BB, is attested in the variant here, while BB used it even though he didn’t have it as a reading in his sources.
#. HTML: <br>
#. VAR: mahantehi → mahattebhi (mr)
msgctxt "an4.25:2.5"
msgid "Esa maggo mahantehi, "
msgstr "This is the path followed by the great souls, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an4.25:2.6"
msgid "anuyāto mahesibhi. "
msgstr "the great hermits. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "an4.25:3.1"
msgid "Ye ca taṃ paṭipajjanti, "
msgstr "Those who practice it "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an4.25:3.2"
msgid "yathā buddhena desitaṃ; "
msgstr "as it was taught by the Buddha, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an4.25:3.3"
msgid "Dukkhassantaṃ karissanti, "
msgstr "doing the teacher’s bidding, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an4.25:3.4"
msgid "satthusāsanakārino”ti. "
msgstr "make an end of suffering.” "

#. HTML: </p></blockquote><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an4.25:3.5"
msgid "Pañcamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
